# solo-triage — environment variables
#
# Copy to .env and fill in. Load with: `set -a; . ./.env; set +a`.
#
# One Telegram bot, scoped to the manager. Approvals from anywhere in
# the team — including inbox's outbound-email drafts — surface here.
#
# Create the bot via @BotFather and paste the token below. Find your
# chat id with @userinfobot.

# ─── Manager bot (reaches `manager`, surfaces all approvals) ──────────
TEAMCTL_TG_MANAGER_TOKEN="123456:AAH-manager-bot-token"
TEAMCTL_TG_MANAGER_CHATS="123456789"
